The '''Spira Regatta''' was an annual [[Yacht/Legends|yacht]] race around the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Spira/Legends|Spira]]. Every year, [[The galaxy/Legends|galactic]] celebrities, [[Diplomat/Legends|diplomats]], wealthy citizens, and the media would go to [[Ataria City]] in anticipation of the event.

[[Aneash Maglea]] was the regatta's reigning champion.

Several known attendees of the regatta included [[Castion Vogol]], [[Tovir Daglear]], [[Ganth]], and [[Darby Willers]].

